<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Thank You | KisanVikas</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/CSS/con.css">
</head>
<style>/* General Styles */
body {
    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f6f9f5;
    color: #333;
  }
  
  .header {
    background-color: #6ebe71;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  
  .header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.5em;
  }
  
  .header p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  
  /* Contact Section */
  .contact-section, .thankyou-section {
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  
  .contact-container, .thankyou-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: auto;
    background-color: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  /* Headings and Text */
  h2 {
    color: #286029;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  /* Form Styles */
  .contact-form .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .contact-form label {
    display: block;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  
  .contact-form input,
  .contact-form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 1em;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  
  .contact-form textarea {
    resize: vertical;
  }
  
  /* Submit Button and Link Button */
  .btn-submit {
    background-color: #286029;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    font-size: 1em;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .btn-submit:hover {
    background-color: #286029;
  }
  
  /* Contact Info Box */
  .contact-info {
    margin-top: 40px;
    background-color: #f0f5f0;
    padding: 20px;
    border-left: 4px solid #286029;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #e0e0e0;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }
  </style>
<body>

  <header class="header">
    <h1>KisanVikas</h1>
    <p>Empowering Farmers, Shaping Futures</p>
  </header>

  <section class="thankyou-section">
    <div class="thankyou-container">
      <h2>Thank You!</h2>
      <p>Your message has been successfully recorded.</p>
      <p>We appreciate you reaching out to us. Our team will review your query and get back to you as soon as possible if needed.</p>
      <a href="/index" class="btn-submit">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 KisanVikas. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
